    <div class="list-text">
    <a
    class="hed-heading -excerpt"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2018/12/27/foreign-policy-our-top-stories-of-2018/">
    <h3 class="hed">Our Top Stories of 2018</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">From the Mueller investigation to China’s expanding influence, these are the pieces readers clicked on the most.</p>
