    class="hed-heading -excerpt"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2018/12/26/despite-rebound-markets-remain-spooked-by-trumpnomics/">
    <h3 class="hed">Investors are Jittery and the Reason is Trump</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">From the U.S. president’s embrace of tariffs to his war with the Fed, some are calling this the “Trump Slump.”</p>
