    <h3 class="hed">Mattis’s Resignation Isn’t a Crisis Yet—But It Probably Will Be</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">The U.S. secretary of defense was right to resign in protest, but Trump can’t handle the consequences.</p>
</div>
