        class="author">
    Ronald R. Krebs</a><span class="separator">,</span> <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/robert-ralston/"
        rel="author"
        class="author">
    Robert Ralston</a><span class="separator">,</span> <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/aaron-rapport/"
        rel="author"
        class="author">
    Aaron Rapport</a></address>

</div>
