    <a
    class="hed-heading -excerpt"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2018/11/26/the-vulgar-marxism-of-middle-east-punditry/">
    <h3 class="hed">The Vulgar Marxism of Middle East Punditry</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">For political activists in the Muslim world, it&#039;s not just the economy, stupid.</p>
